(secondQuint)4XL Study - Obesity Surgery in Adolescence.

 The study has two intervention arms: Experimental: Group A Surgery; laparoscopic gastric bypass Active comparator: Group B Patients from Child Obesity Registry of Vestfold who get standard conservative treatment in a multidisiplinary team at Morbid Obesity Center.

 All patients are referred to Morbid Obesity Center from other hospitals or general practionairs in Norway.

 The procedure will take place at the Vestfold Hospital Trust The participants are included for 2 years follow-up with visits to a multidisciplinary team every 3rd month at the Morbid Obesity Center.

 Total follow-up time is ten years.

